<div class="description">
    <h3>Description</h3>

    <div class="body">
        <p>Because of strong typing in the Zend_Dojo_View_Helper_Button class, function button(), argument 4 is null when a decorator is set.</p>

<p>Same with SubmitButton, others not checked.</p>

<p>$this-&gt;addElement ( 'Button', 'closeBtn', array ('label' =&gt; 'Close', 'class' =&gt; 'CloseBtn', 'decorators' =&gt; array ( 'ViewHelper' ) ) );</p>

<p>-- or --
$this-&gt;addElement ( 'Button', 'closeBtn', array ('label' =&gt; 'Close', 'class' =&gt; 'CloseBtn' ) );
$this-&gt;setElementDecorators( array ('ViewHelper' ) );</p>

    </div>
