        <div class="comment">
        <p class="metadata">Posted by Matthew Weier O'Phinney (matthew) on 2011-05-02T17:22:14.000+0000</p> 
        <div class="body">
            <p>You <em>can</em> use any decorator, but we can't <em>guarantee</em> that it will work if you use something other than DijitElement when using Dojo form elements. I'm closing as "won't fix", as the solution is simply to use DijitElement instead of ViewHelper as the decorator.</p>

